voicelines.text: Sorry lad, ye aren't getting in here with that state ye'r in.
Woah now. Can't let ye in with that attire. This party is for bone-heads only.
Sorry lad, no skin allowed beyond this point. Come have a go again when ye've peeled it off.
Sorry laddie, can't let ye in. You're violating the dress code. Shed the skin and come back.
Sorry lad, ye aren't gettin in here with that state ye'r in. Come back when ye've lost ye'r skin.
You're not on the list. Bugger off.
Get out of here, sour-face.
Yer still ere? Either peel it, or beat it.
Scram! Ye're not invited!
\**HOHOHO*\* WE'RE DOING IT THE SOLID WAY THEN! ALRIGHT!
ALRIGHT! HERE WE GO!
OI, THOSE EARS O' YOUS WORK? GET BACK ERE!
WHAT ARE YE, A TWO TIMING TROGLODYTE? YOU'RE NOT PERMITTED INTO THIS PARTY!
WHO DO YE THINK YE ARE, WISE GUY!? YOU. DO NOT! HAVE PERMISSION!! TO ENTER THIS PARTY!!!
Breaks over I suppose.
OH LOVELY! WE'RE DEALING WITH A MOR-OOOONNN!!! GET BACK HERE YE DEADBEAT!
ARE YE DEAF LAD? YE'R NOT. INVITED. TO THIS PARTY!
Good! Stay out!
Come back when ye've learned to read, ya nimwit!
And don't come back!
And stay out, ye frollocking fleshbag!
Now BEAT it! I don't wanna see ye again!
YOU WON'T GET AWAY FROM ME THAT EASY, YE PILFERING PARASITES!
GET BACK 'ERE', YOU RAT!
YER A GOWK FOR RUNNING, PAL!
COME HERE, YE PILFERING SWINE!
YOU THINK YOU CAN OUTRUN ME!?
YOU NEED TO VACATE THE PREMISE, IMMEDIATELY!
YOU. ARE VIOLATING. THE DRESS CODE!
YER NOTHING BUT A SOUR-BONED SASSONACK!
STAY DOWN!
STAY DOWN, IF YE KNOW WHATS BEST FOR YE!
DOWN YE GO!
EVIL SKELETON PUNCH!
TAKE THIS, YE BLOODY VERMIN!
OPEN THE GATE! YE BLISTERING BARNACLES!
Don't look so sour-faced now, lad! Ye fit right in!
Thank ye laddie. You may now, enjoy the party!
Ey!! Now yer followin' the dress code!
